[normal]Gregory Barker:[bold] But it does not have to be domestic heating. Industrial heat from power stations can sometimes be more appropriate. If you have a power station, it makes sense to co-locate large industrial sites next to it. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q227[bold] 
